modName: Miss Blue preset for race menu
summary: Just a preset for my miss blue
descriptionHtml:
This is just a preset version of my character and follower miss blue , i changed the ears slightly. 

Main credit to [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/29658810]wnisewond[/url] for his gorgeous preset mods , without them miss blue wouldn't be here ;) I can not stress this enough if you lack inspiration and skill on creating characters please check him out! Great starter base for characters and absolutely beautiful faces 


This is my FIRST preset mod so I hope it works. Feedback appreciated and welcome :) Just be gentle Im still very new. 

you will need all the required mods im sure to get her full look.
